body_text:
@pjh5, Thanks. I have installed NCCL using conda since I am using a conda environment. Anaconda provides installation for NCCL. conda install -c anaconda nccl
Also, I ran:
conda install -c caffe2 caffe2-cuda9.0-cudnn7-gcc4.8 in case I was missing out on gcc

body:
@pjh5, Thanks. I have installed NCCL using conda since I am using a conda environment. Anaconda provides installation for NCCL. `conda install -c anaconda nccl`

Also, I ran: 
`conda install -c caffe2 caffe2-cuda9.0-cudnn7-gcc4.8` in case I was missing out on gcc
